OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FThe daughter of Lesley Howell - who
OL,8,Fwas murdered over 30 years ago at the
OL,9,Fhands of her husband - has talked of
OL,10,Fhow she is "rediscovering" her mum
OL,11,Fafter first believing she died in a
OL,12,Fsuicide pact for almost 20 years.
OL,14,FDr Lauen Bradford-Clarke said said
OL,15,Fwanted to do as much as she could to
OL,16,F"honour" her mum.
