OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FIn May 1991, police originally thought
OL,8,Fthe deaths of Lesley Howell and Trevor
OL,9,FBuchanan were suicide after their
OL,10,Fbodies were found in a fume-filled
OL,11,Fgarage in Castlerock. It was thought
OL,12,Fthey took their lives after
OL,13,Fdiscovering their partners were having
OL,14,Fan extra-marital affair.
OL,16,FHowever, 18 years later, Lesley's then-
OL,17,Fhusband, Colin, walked into a police
OL,18,Fstation and confessed to murdering
OL,19,Fthem. He also implicated his Hazel
OL,20,FStewart in the killings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
