OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FTheir victims had actually been
OL,8,Fdrugged and murdered with their bodies
OL,9,Farranged to appear as if they had
OL,10,Fcommitted suicide.
OL,12,FColin and Lesley's daughter, Lauren
OL,13,FBradford-Clarke, shared her story,
OL,14,Falong with her siblings in a new ITV
OL,15,Fdocumentary 'Killer in the House'.
OL,17,FOn This Morning she spoke of the
OL,18,F"shocking moments" when she found out
OL,19,Fthe truth of her mother's murder.
