OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,FShe said: "There's so much that I
OL,8,Fcan't even articulate about it because
OL,9,Fof how shocking it was."
OL,11,FLauren was just four years old when
OL,12,Fshe learned her mother had died.
OL,14,F"I grew up fearful of car fumes. If
OL,15,Fanyone was walking near the back of a
OL,16,Fcar, I'd say: 'Don't go there,' and be
OL,17,Falmost panicked," she recalled.
OL,19,FLauren said the story of her mum's
OL,20,Fsuicide "didn't make sense" to her.
