OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,F"I had such an inherent sense of who
OL,8,Fshe was as a mother without really
OL,9,Fhaving an explanation for that because
OL,10,FI was so young."
OL,12,FShe added: "I still can't understand
OL,13,Fit, and I felt that then. But there
OL,14,Fwas an immediate sense, in the midst
OL,15,Fof that shock, that 'It makes more
OL,16,Fsense,' and I can't explain that.
