OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,F"I grew up raised by my father, always
OL,8,Fthought it was suicide, and I had this
OL,9,Finstant sense of, 'That makes more
OL,10,Fsense,' and I cannot explain that,
OL,11,Fother than, that's the impression that
OL,12,Fmy mum had already implanted on me in
OL,13,Fsuch a short time that she would never
OL,14,Fhave left her children."
OL,16,FLauren said she now doesn't "spend
OL,17,Fenergy or time thinking about that".
