OL,3,C'I want to honour her': Lesley Howell
OL,4,Cdaughter talks of 'rediscovering' her
OL,5,Cmum
OL,7,F"So much of my focus has been on
OL,8,Frediscovering my mum, in lots of ways
OL,9,Fdiscovering her for the first time,
OL,10,Fand the restoration of her whole
OL,11,Fidentity has shifted now that she
OL,12,Fdidn't kill herself," she said.
OL,14,F"Life is precious, and I want to do as
OL,15,Fmuch as I can to honour her."
